               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400203-name-449" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-449" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-449" type="surname" value="MORTON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-449" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE MORTON</persName>
                  </hi>. I live at No. 74, York-street, Westminster. Be<lb></lb>tween</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184002030060"></xptr>
               <p>five and six o'clock in the evening of the 21st of January I observed the prisoner take a counterpane off Mr. Phillips's bed, she dropped it, took it up again, and took it away—she came towards me, and said Mr. Phillips bad offered her 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. for it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400203-name-450" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-450" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-450" type="surname" value="PHILLIPS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-450" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN PHILLIPS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a broker, and live in Great Chapel-street, West<lb></lb>minster. A little boy came and told me something—I ran out and could not see this woman—I ran to the corner of a back entrance, which goes to another street, and saw the prisoner with a large bundle—I asked what she had got—she said, "Two loaves and some bacon, and this counter<lb></lb>pane" "—I asked where she had got it—she said a little girl gave it her—it is mine.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400203-name-451" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-451" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
